            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> Prisciano <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> provinciae <lb n="4"/>Pannoniae <lb n="5"/>superioris <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> regni Norici <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> XX hereditatium <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> provinciae <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">Mauretaniae Caesariensis</supplied> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>n<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>io<lb break="no" n="11"/>rius Severus <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/>Sigambro<lb break="no" n="14"/>rum praepo<lb break="no" n="15"/>situs clas<lb break="no" n="16"/>sibus <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nach der Prokuratur des Geehrten in Noricum (168 n. Chr.) u. der darauffolgenden Ausübung des Amtes des proc. XX hereditatium, als Claudius Priscianus Prokurator der Mauretania Caesariensis war.</p>
            </div>
